title: 650C 45mm Micro Wheelset
body_html:
This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix Cycles

Designed for speed and style in a more compact package, these Pure Fix double-walled aluminum wheelsets are size 650C with a 45mm rim depth, front and rear. Our wheels include name-brand and laser-etched, 120 mm KT Quando hubs. Our rear wheels include flip-flop hubs with a pre-attached 16T fixed cog along with a 16T freewheel cog for single-speed riding. Front and rear wheels feature 32 spokes each and all wheelsets include nylon rim-strips to protect against sharp edges and prevent tube puncture.

We recommend using any style of 650C tire (tires and tubes not included).

List of Specs:

  • 650C
  • 45mm rim depth
  • Double-walled aluminum
  • 120mm KT Quando hubs
  • Non-sealed
  • Flip-flop rear hub
  • Comes with pre-attached 16T fixed and freewheel cog
  • 32 spokes per wheel
  • Includes nylon rim strips
  • 3.5 lbs per wheel
  • Perfect for our Micro Line

title: Aviator + Afterburner
body_html:
This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix Cycles

Your lights should last forever. Weather, thieves, bumpy roads, dead batteries; there’s a seemingly endless list of things that can cut the lives of lights short, so Fortified designed their Aviator/Afterburner combo to be a pair that never needs to be replaced. Waterproof, shockproof, rechargeable, and mounted with custom bolts to prevent theft, this dynamic duo is ready for whatever the streets throw their way. The best part? Fortified is so committed to the concept that their lights should last forever that if anything does defeat them, they’ll replace ‘em for you! These are the last lights you'll ever need to buy.

Forever Promise

Custom bolts lock the lights to your frame, while an aluminum fuselage makes them waterproof and shockproof. And if anything does ever happen to them, we replace 'em.

USB Rechargeable

We spent nearly 2 years engineering a custom cell that works for the city. To recharge, simply pop out the special battery and plug it into any USB port.

Extended Battery

To keep recharging to a minimum, we focused on milliamp hours and circuit efficiency.

body_html:

You’re a fast mother@#$%^&, but how fast? You stack miles like a lumberjack stacks pancakes, but how many? Your rides are good for the environment, but how good? Along with a pretty nifty clock, you get real-time access to your current, average, and max speed, total and trip distance, elapsed time, calories burnt, and even your environmental carbon offset! title: Chamois Butt'r
body_html:
This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix Cycles

Chamois Butt’r® is the Original non-greasy chamois cream and the favorite of professional and recreational cyclists.

Developed in 1988 by Steve Mathews, a cyclist and Physical Therapist, in conjunction with chemists, physicians and professional cyclists, Chamois Butt’r® sets the standard for high quality chamois creams in the US.

Manufactured with only the highest quality ingredients adhering to the FDA’s Good Manufacturing Practice (GMP) guidelines, Chamois Butt’r® products are paraben free, gluten free and contain no artificial colors or fragrances.

DIRECTIONS:

Apply liberally to skin and chamois before each ride. May be applied to any skin areas that rub together or against clothing.

title: Harding
body_html:
This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix Cycles

The Pure Fix Premium Series is the perfect bike to take your riding to the next level.  Featuring a double-butted 4130 chromoly frame, the Premium Series was bred to be lighter, stiffer, and faster.  It comes street-ready with wrapped drop bars, our 700C, 30mm wheelset featuring sealed bearing hubs and a machined braking surface, and includes Thickslick 700x28c tires standard.  The raked chrome fork and polished silver quill stem and seat help bring a dash of classic style to a bike that's guaranteed to turn heads, warm hearts, and haul ass.

title: High Pressure Rim Tape
body_html:
This is a demonstration store. You can purchase products like this from Pure Fix Cycles

The more you ride, the more your wheels wear, and the more this wear comes into contact with the tube, leading to ruptures.  Our rim tape was developed to give extra protection from flats, creating a solid barrier between the tube and wheel, keeping your tires free from flats and your bike on the road instead of on your back.  A definite must have for any urban rider.
